snippet.title: Super BAWK BAWK Chicken Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
A new trailer for our game Super BAWK BAWK Chicken the free demo soon to be released on steam!
Super BAWK BAWK Chicken is a fast-paced infinite runner with a cute and quirky vibe. Play as a chicken with super powers; Jump, Dash, and BAWK your way to a new high score.

Super BAWK BAWK Chicken will be releasing to Steam Q3, 2023.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2054850/Super_BAWK_BAWK_Chicken/
Wishlist Super BAWK BAWK Chicken on Steam today!

Join our Discord and follow our progress!
